item.title: asakura
item.description: Asakura is real estate brand from Japan that specializes in the sale of apartments, including new and luxury ones. Asakura has been a part of the Japanese market since the 1960, and they have a good reputation for their service and their apartments. Asakura offers a wide range of properties, from townhouses to luxury apartments, so there is something for everyone. They also specialize in luxury apartments in Tokyo, so if you are looking for something more than just a starter apartment, you will find what you need here.
